00:46:06.910 --> 00:46:08.740
to the economic growth in Russia,

00:46:08.820 --> 00:46:13.040
which has been recorded since 2004.

00:46:13.660 --> 00:46:16.000
Within the framework of economic theory,

00:46:16.010 --> 00:46:17.640
it has always been proven that

00:46:17.650 --> 00:46:20.020
as soon as the gross domestic product

00:46:20.030 --> 00:46:22.420
of a country begins to grow, not only

00:46:22.430 --> 00:46:24.320
