has become a member of the World

00:54:16.000 --> 00:54:17.810
Trade Organization receives.

00:54:18.470 --> 00:54:20.810
The first goal is to obtain

00:54:20.820 --> 00:54:22.690
non-discriminatory conditions

00:54:22.700 --> 00:54:24.730
for access to foreign markets

00:54:24.740 --> 00:54:27.550
