00:54:45.060 --> 00:54:49.690
for settling trade disputes, which

00:54:49.700 --> 00:54:52.590
is well-developed within

00:54:52.600 --> 00:54:54.570
the framework of the World Trade

00:54:54.580 --> 00:54:55.630
Organization, is very important

00:54:55.640 --> 00:54:57.990
for Russia and is not accidentally

00:54:58.000 --> 00:54:59.550
used by more and more

00:54:59.560 --> 00:55:03.030
WTO member countries.

00:55:04.270 --> 00:55:06.270
On the other hand, if we become

00:55:06.280 --> 00:55:09.150
members of the WTO, it means that

00:55:09.160 --> 00:55:12.410
most countries in the world do

00:55:12.420 --> 00:55:15.210
not conflict with us on trade

00:55:15.220 --> 00:55:17.510
and other positions that fall

00:55:17.520 --> 00:55:19.930
within the jurisdiction

00:55:19.940 --> 00:55:21.110
of the WTO.

00:55:21.690 --> 00:55:24.010
Our foreign

00:55:24.020 --> 00:55:26.130
policy is becoming

00:55:26.140 --> 00:55:28.570
more predictable.

00:55:30.410 --> 00:55:32.650
When countries join the World Trade

00:55:32.660 --> 00:55:34.290
Organization, one of the requirements

00:55:34.300 --> 00:55:37.010
in the WTO process is the harmonization

00:55:37.020 --> 00:55:41.610
of domestic laws with WTO rules

00:55:41.620 --> 00:55:43.650
and norms, with international

00:55:43.660 --> 00:55:45.870
standards.

00:55:46.110 --> 00:55:47.690
International standards

00:55:47.700 --> 00:55:49.770
envisage the liberalization

00:55:49.930 --> 00:55:52.970
of domestic legislation in

00:55:52.980 --> 00:55:55.430
relation to foreign investors.

00:55:55.470 --> 00:55:57.370
Thus, creating a favorable

00:55:57.380 --> 00:55:59.010
clearing for investment is

00:55:59.020 --> 00:56:02.670
also one of the goals of Russia'

00:56:02.680 --> 00:56:04.350
s accession to the WTO.

